data.description: Are you searching for a beautiful and well maintained home that is move-in ready and offers a large fully fenced in yard? If so, there is no need to look any further.  This home has never flooded, is in flood zone X, beautiful landscaping, freshly painted, no carpet, features a kitchen with a corner sink, breakfast room, as well as a formal dining room, spacious living room, crown moulding, gas log fireplace, a huge backyard with an electric gate to access the yard and rear carport. Can you picture yourself sitting around the awesome in-ground fire pit and relaxing on those chilly days? There are too many features to list. This one is a must see! Call me to schedule your showing today as this won't last long!
